        correct: 1,
        rationale: "Presenting absolute risk with context (benefits AND harms) is the gold standard for risk communication in SDM. Relative risk (20% reduction) sounds impressive but is misleading without the baseline context. Absolute numbers allow patients to make truly informed decisions."
